description: SendSMTP project conventions (Wails 3, React, SQLite, goscan)
alwaysApply: true
---

# SendSMTP

- Desktop: Wails v3 + React/TS + Tailwind (shadcn-style components in `frontend/src/components/ui`).
- Engine: Go packages under `internal/` shared by UI (`app.go`) and CLI (`cmd/sendsmtp`).
- Config: `app.config.yml` (not `build/config.yml`, which is Wails packaging).
- DB: SQLite at path from config (`data/sendsmtp.db`).
- SMTP import:
  - Goscan blocks starting with `--- SMTP config (goscan) ---`.
  - Or `email;password` lines → `smtpdiscover` uses MX fingerprints (e.g. Locaweb → `email-ssl.com.br`) and verifies AUTH.
  - `from` / `user` must be real emails — `${MAIL_USERNAME}` is not expanded; sanitized in `mailer.SanitizeFrom` / `ResolveFrom`.
- IMAP extract (SMTPs → Extract contacts): discovers IMAP, scrapes INBOX/Sent for contacts + `email;password`, writes `data/extracted/`, imports contacts into the email queue and creds as SMTPs.
- Templates: `data/msg.html`, `data/assuntos.txt` (see `data/README.md`).
- Placeholders: `{{email}}`, `{{link}}`, `{{assunto}}`, `{{subject}}`, `{{from}}`, `{{uniq}}`, `{{id}}`.
- On send, `{{link}}` is personalized via `mailer.PersonalizeLink` → `base/?p=<email>` (URL-encoded). Do not hardcode `?p=` in templates or `links.txt`.
- Optional footer From: `<span data-from>{{from}}</span>` (omitted when From empty/unresolved).
- Spintax: `{a|b|c}` — requires `|`; `{Status}` alone stays literal.
- Email import: always normalize + dedupe; optional DNS validate is paced (not a DNS flood). Large lists: Import file, not paste.
- Email list: `ListEmailsPage(filter, query, limit, offset)`; UNIQUE address — no re-send to already-stored/sent. Status counts via `email_counts`.
- Do not commit secrets: `data/smtps.txt`, `data/sendsmtp.db`, `data/extracted/`, passwords, server SSH/SOCKS creds.
- Servers (egress): page `/servers` — import `IP|password`, deploy SOCKS5 on free port near prefer (default 10808) via SSH; campaign dials SMTP through active SOCKS so egress is the VPS IP.
- Bindings: regenerate with `wails3 generate bindings -ts -d frontend/bindings ./...`
- Dev: `wails3 dev` / `task dev`. Rebuild SOCKS embed: `task socks5d`. CLI: `go build -o bin/sendsmtp-cli ./cmd/sendsmtp`.
- **i18n**: all UI copy via `useTranslation()` / `t("key")` from `@/i18n`. Catalogs `frontend/src/i18n/locales/{en,pt}.ts`. Language switch in Settings. See skill `.cursor/skills/sendsmtp-i18n`. Never hardcode user-facing strings in React components.
